<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Pricing - MigsList</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    .pricing-page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
    }
    .pricing-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .pricing-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .pricing-header p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .pricing-content {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: -3rem auto 0;
      padding: 0 2rem 4rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    .pricing-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 3rem;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto 3rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .price {
      font-size: 4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1e40af;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .price-period {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: #6b7280;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .pricing-card .btn {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      padding: 1rem 3rem;
    }
    .features-section {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }
    .features-section h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #1f2937;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .feature-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .feature-card h3 {
      color: #1f2937;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      background: #dbeafe;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #2563eb;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .feature-card p {
      color: #6b7280;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .included-list {
      text-align: left;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }
    .included-list li {
      padding: 0.5rem 0;
      color: #374151;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }
    .included-list li::before {
      content: "âœ“";
      color: #16a34a;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .nav-simple {
      background: transparent;
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .nav-simple a {
      color: white;
    }
    .nav-simple .brand {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .cta-section {
      background: #1e40af;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
    }
    .cta-section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .cta-section p {
      opacity: 0.9;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    .cta-section .btn {
      background: white;
      color: #1e40af;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      padding: 1rem 3rem;
    }
    .cta-section .btn:hover {
      background: #f1f5f9;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="pricing-page">
  <div class="pricing-header">
    <nav class="nav-simple">
      <a href="/" class="brand">MigsList</a>
      <a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline" style="border-color: white; color: white;">Sign In</a>
    </nav>
    <h1>Simple, Transparent Pricing</h1>
    <p>Everything your union needs to manage member lists and track good standing status.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pricing-content">
    <div class="pricing-card">
      <div class="price">$400</div>
      <div class="price-period">per year</div>

      <ul class="included-list">
        <li>Unlimited buckets</li>
        <li>Unlimited members</li>
        <li>PDF document uploads</li>
        <li>Good standing tracking</li>
        <li>Excel export reports</li>
        <li>Multiple admin accounts</li>
        <li>Secure data storage</li>
        <li>Email support</li>
      </ul>

      <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
    </div>

    <section class="features-section">
      <h2>Everything You Need</h2>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3><span class="feature-icon">1</span> Organize by Buckets</h3>
          <p>Create buckets to organize members by category, department, or any grouping that makes sense for your local. Each bucket tracks its own member list.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3><span class="feature-icon">2</span> Track Member Info</h3>
          <p>Store member details including name, email, phone, and mailing address. Perfect for locals that need to reach members who don't have email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3><span class="feature-icon">3</span> Document Upload</h3>
          <p>Upload signed PDF documents for each member. When a member submits their signed paperwork, upload it and they're automatically marked as "in good standing."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3><span class="feature-icon">4</span> Good Standing Reports</h3>
          <p>Export Excel reports of members in good standing with one click. Perfect for submitting to your international or for internal record keeping.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3><span class="feature-icon">5</span> Search & Find</h3>
          <p>Quickly search across all your buckets to find any member by name or email. No more digging through spreadsheets.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3><span class="feature-icon">6</span> Secure Access</h3>
          <p>Your data is protected with industry-standard security. Create multiple admin accounts so your team can share the workload.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Ready to Get Organized?</h2>
    <p>Join other union locals using MigsList to streamline their member management.</p>
    <a href="/signup" class="btn">Sign Up Now - $400/year</a>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
